snippet.title: Back From Hell Trailer - Photoplay Games (update)
snippet.description:
Photoplay Games is creating Back From Hell, it's an CRPG Puzzle Adventure game set in 15th Century central Spain and the afterlife of Hell. You can follow us at

http://www.backfromhellgame.com/
https://twitter.com/photoplaygames
https://www.facebook.com/backfromhellgame/
